description:
Light and stretchy convertible pants to keep your options open when hiking, camping or travelling. A gusseted crotch and knee darts give you room for stepping over logs or sprinting along train station platforms. Lots of pockets keep your camera and maps within reach and safely tucked away.Made of stretch-woven nylon and spandex with a DWR (durable water repellency) finish to shed water and dirt.Fabric provides UPF 50+ protection.Articulated knees and gussetted crotch allow unrestricted movement.Jeans-like hand pockets and top stitched rear pockets.1 zippered and 1 envelope cargo pocket provide extra storage.Zippers convert them to shorts(with a 10-inch inseam) colour-coded zippers help you re-attach them correctly.

